09.to check for number is armstrong 

pseudo :routine
function Armstrong(num){
    temp = num
    sum = 0
    while temp > 0 do
      rem = tem % 10
      sum = sum + rem ^ no_of_digits
      temp = temp /10

    if sum == num
      return true
    else
      return false
}

pseudo :routine test:
function testArmstrong(){
    input num
    if Armstrong(num)
      print("the given number is armstrong")
    else
      print("the given number is not armstrong)
}
pseudo: test routine in the driver code / main function 
function __Main__(){
    testArmstrong()
}
